title: The James Cotton Band 100% Cotton

James Cotton 100% Cotton CDRIP  
Category Rock/Pop, Chicago Blues, Blues

Personnel: James Cotton (vocals, harmonica); Little Bo (saxophone); Lenny Baker (baritone saxophone); Phil Jekanowski (piano); Charles Calmese (bass); Kenny Johnson (drums).

All songs written by James Cotton or Mat "Guitar" Murphy, except "Rocket 88" (Jacki Brenston), "I Don&#039;t Know" (Willie Mabon) and "Fever" (Eddie Cooley/John Davenport).
